{"tid":1399285,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大戰前夕]留意到728 49人被捕後 好多人屈前線係無腦送頭On9仔 前線從來唔係磨爛蓆賴死唔走","createTime":"2019-08-03T06:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T11:55:37.000Z","uid":1889,"like":19,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf5c39d41d77cdba71b1db696f517588b4c33ae","tid":1399285,"uid":1889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">前線既手足意念一直好清 就係每個人都係有自己既獨立思考</span><br />\n你想幾時走就幾時走 你想留到幾時就留到幾時<br />\n唔好再拎立法會抬人走嚟打飛機<br />\n立法會係室內兼非公眾地方 你冇任何藉口理由出現係果到 <br />\n一比差佬包圍左就宣告100%被捕 兼 必定重罪<br />\n所以果日先會堅持要一個不留 一齊走<br />\n但唔好將立法會果日既情況推到去街頭戰 <br />\n街頭戰從來冇明確line話幾時走就叫合理 <br />\n<br />\n你覺得差佬facebook講 即將有清場消息 離遠望到格警車已經要走 咁你咪果時走囉<br />\n你覺得同差佬仲有200米距離慢慢行過嚟已經好危險 咁你咪果時走囉<br />\n你覺得東南西北 有兩面比人圍左好撚危險要走既 你咪果時走囉<br />\n你覺得同差佬少過50米對峙 除時一衝上嚟就被捕走唔切 咁你咪果時走囉<br />\n你覺得自己跑得好撚快 差佬隻手臨掂到你果刻先走都走得切 你咪果時先走囉<br />\n你覺得自己老豆做大律師比人捉都唔驚 或者你覺得咁樣判坐十碌叫意義既 你咪唔撚走囉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我上個post曾經講過三大徹退條件 有人唔同意 其實絕對係100%好事<br />\n因為呢個就係我地前線想見到既野 就係大家識獨立思考 人人有自己把尺<br />\n唔會我叫你留你就跟人留 人地叫你走就跟人走 冇哂自己思想意志</span><br />\n我地從來無鼓勵人留到2046 亦無鼓吹過任何增加被捕風險行為<br />\n根本個個人幾時應該走條line就唔同 我地前線鼓勵既 係兄弟爬山<br />\n大家自己獨立思考 好好衡量風險 覺得留守有用既就留 覺得被捕風險高既就走<br />\n之後就好撚鍾意講 「咁你地即係送頭啦 下次抬佢地走！」<br />\n「後排就係見你唔走 佢地先唔捨得走陪你 你而家害鳩埋人地啦」<br />\n唔好意思 咁你係應該同後排留守既人講 要衡量好風險要識自己走<br />\n鼓勵每個人 不論係企最前 中間 定 後排 都有自己獨立思考<br />\n而唔係屌番想留到最後一刻 真係再唔走就比人拉先走 既人 陷佢地於不於話佢地害鳩人<br />\n我地前線最唔撚鋸既 就係永遠有班冷氣軍師覺得自己條line一定係最啱<br />\n一定要全世界都跟佢果條line 佢覺得幾時走係最佳最機就要全世界跟佢一齊幾時走<br />\n唔跟佢就係送頭 就係弱智柒 <span style=\"color: red;\">我地鼓勵既 係每個人有自己獨立思考</span><br />\n嚟緊相信仲有好多場大戰 希望前線中間後排家中各位共勉之。"},{"pid":"c7dc6cc17df1dbc84dfa5d2ecdd9d5f6a47f58de","tid":1399285,"uid":16063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:14:38.000Z","msg":"同埋講真上次係窄巷　<br />\n後面塞死哂　前面又追打<br />\n咪即係第一原則　前有追兵後冇退路　要徹<br />\n其實都冇錯 果時係應該走 起碼出番大街先<br />\n有邊個想4比人拉 最緊要係比人拉左之後唔好搵戰犯互屌<br />\n諗下之後點做好啲就OK"},{"pid":"583d2facecfbbcb019c8c3f77f3a21088fdf8e09","tid":1399285,"uid":91721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"格硬整一啲撤退規則<br />\n其實就係教條主義<br />\n放棄思考"},{"pid":"dd913d683c8927c1d67d2b969a2d8ab01de88911","tid":1399285,"uid":37220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"583d2facecfbbcb019c8c3f77f3a21088fdf8e09","tid":1399285,"uid":91721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"格硬整一啲撤退規則<br />\n其實就係教條主義<br />\n放棄思考"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:17:33.000Z","msg":"exactly"},{"pid":"4e37e0b6b1d76ffe9d11828d0d1782f33ccbaccf","tid":1399285,"uid":219244,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"問題係依家黑警已經轉左策略<br />\n玩圍捕<br />\n<br />\n前線繼續留到最後一刻會有好大風險<br />\n同埋去到錢先就會知<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以否定前線有一批人好撚戀戰</span></strong>，而且情緒好激動，好緊張<br />\n現場氣氛係會令到叫極都唔肯走，仲會郁啲就屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬呀， 設立哨兵嘅目的就係知道黑警去到邊，幾時要散同埋撤退路線<br />\n如果點都諗住短兵交接嘅話，咁要哨兵做咩<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔希望每個星期都要去法院一次聲援被捕人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望前線義士可以以大局為重<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>凡事冷靜</strong></span><br />\n諗清楚自己個行動對成個運動有乜影響<br />\n而家唔只係你哋個人承唔承受得起被捕，係香港承受唔起失去你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望唔好濫用「尊重前線」<br />\n<br />\n特別想講係以往金鐘我哋同警察都好熟路<br />\n但係過去幾次轉左落地佢之後<br />\n尤其去元朗同西上環<br />\n每次衝突都牽涉幾條街，範圍好大<br />\n但大部份前線手足都淨係掛住自己條街嘅狀況<br />\n老實講，好容易隔離街失手守都唔知，或者有啲小巷突然有速龍沖出嚟，變相好容易被捕<br />\n<br />\n好似元朗果次咁，明明大馬路都撤到佢鳳翔街<br />\n 但係大坑渠嘅手足仲留喺原地，都真係幾危險<br />\n<br />\n所以大家真係要Be Water<br />\n因為呢個係長期抗戰，唔係一兩次就可以定勝負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後好感謝前線嘅付出"},{"pid":"ce8bc4f0dfb49c4294dcfd6df8f0374632564571","tid":1399285,"uid":45123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"好多都扮理性實分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係都請大家自我保護要緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff17ab3e5c9567d83702dd0bae07f6dd71311bc","tid":1399285,"uid":207202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"我淨係希望前線醒水<br />\n唔係一定要等到對面放催淚彈開槍先走得<br />\n我地同對家實力太懸殊<br />\n難道真係唔可以玩游擊？<br />\n有時候大家都要能屈能伸d<br />\n要正視自己實力究竟同對家差幾遠<br />\n<br />\n利申：不分化理性討論"},{"pid":"5977d80d05830cfbbcec0e7b0df01e46adafa36d","tid":1399285,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d06d5a35b454638a6af456b762f67106dba817","tid":1399285,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:11:38.000Z","msg":"推比班發悔氣屌鳩人既人睇"},{"pid":"f19f7d592a129157d31774c9aa28bc23d7dc0d7b","tid":1399285,"uid":28451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"樓主對今晚守住個路口，然後一堆手足俾狗打有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非個人意願係俾狗打俾狗捉，否則我睇唔明點解要留守<br />\n利申9點走"},{"pid":"ee7f1c923c410a1872692ff6a121dc0db7ace6e7","tid":1399285,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f19f7d592a129157d31774c9aa28bc23d7dc0d7b","tid":1399285,"uid":28451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"樓主對今晚守住個路口，然後一堆手足俾狗打有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非個人意願係俾狗打俾狗捉，否則我睇唔明點解要留守<br />\n利申9點走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"佔領旺角正式啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba83a599a7c65de958d9807b11281990a4d9187","tid":1399285,"uid":79589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"樓主對於狗仔放哂風大圍捕<br />\n然後仲有人call馬去旺角有咩睇法？<br />\n<br />\n講多次<br />\n<br />\n前線有人戀戰<br />\n現場就會有人做後勤，做first aid<br />\n目的就係唔想你班人比人拉、走去前送頭<br />\n<br />\n唔出再講乜野獨立思考，後勤係一定會顧及前線<br />\n呢啲係團體效應<br />\n到最後往往係後勤兵為救人而比人拉<br />\n值得咩？"},{"pid":"23e9e4a840dab3dc2efbaa02a3a59670a5f3f409","tid":1399285,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:06:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>前線有冇鬼唔係重點，重點係要戰略上防止被帶風向！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1401516/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1401516/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fZNmWz8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZNmWz8.png&h=e182a134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/edrbzmP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedrbzmP.png&h=93abf6e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ec415ead8ca4195b42ff1293e1b5e29443fbc94","tid":1399285,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:07:22.000Z","msg":"又拉咗個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f00110ae75fe111deaa79398da5826f55600e57","tid":1399285,"uid":55552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">獨你老母立思考咩！你前線磨爛蓆唔撚走，後排怕你哋無backup焗住一齊守，最後咪冚家鏟一鑊熟囉！做人咪咁自撚私得唔得</span></span>"},{"pid":"9890fab1d18890a9a150906cd62e756ed80917da","tid":1399285,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:17:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f7b98834b83056cd7821141b2644d36a321deb8","tid":1399285,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a5c491447f4d6326379519a8a29d00ec064d60b","tid":1399285,"uid":130734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:55:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}